# How to get a Gmail App Password:
#   1. Go to https://myaccount.google.com/security
#   2. Enable 2-Step Verification (required)
#   3. Search "App passwords" → create one named "Trading Monitor"
#   4. Copy the 16-character password (no spaces) into SMTP_PASSWORD below

